v6.0.101
- new config to enable viewer.js for office documents (ENABLE_VIEWER_JS in conf/system.conf)

v6.0.100
- new video/audio config-file (/conf/audio-video.conf.php)
- video resolutions & formats now configurable

v6.0.99
- composer for dependency management
- moved H5P-database to mysql/postgres
- H5P admin tools
- use viewer.js for office documents
- videos now use aac for audio
- select video resolution by connection speed
- fullscreen mode for pictures
- support youtube-shortlinks

v5.1
- simplified communications with repository
- video/audio conversion triggered directly by upload
- multiple video resolutions to choose from
- images are prerendered in several resolutions
- support for svg images
- support for webp images
- support for animated gifs
- apps share objects
- only build new cache object if content has changed

